             was indicted for <rs id="t18280911-206-off1057" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18280911-206-off1057" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18280911-206-off1057" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18280911-206-cd1058" type="crimeDate">28th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18280911-206-off1057 t18280911-206-cd1058"></join>, three iron locks, value 7s., and 22 squares of glass, value 30s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18280911-206-victim1189" type="victimName">
                        Thomas 
                        Dunstan
                     <interp inst="t18280911-206-victim1189" type="surname" value="Dunstan"></interp>
